tsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Aart_Bik&amp;action=edit&amp;section=11\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap mw-references-columns\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Capture from the <a href=\"/Chess_for_Android#Video\" title=\"Chess for Android\">Chess for Android - Video</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Aart Bik (<b>1996</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.aartbik.com/MT1/sparse.html\">Compiler Support for Sparse Matrix Computations</a></i>. Ph.D. thesis, <a href=\"/Leiden_University\" title=\"Leiden University\">Leiden University</a>, advisor <a href=\"/Mathematician#Wijshoff\" title=\"Mathematician\">Harry A. G. Wijshoff</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.aartbik.com/MISC/chess.html\">Aart's Computer Chess Page</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.aartbik.com/MISC/uchess.html\">UCI and XBoard Protocols for Android</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=53225\">Chess for Glass</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Aart Bik</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, August 08, 2014</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><